    <section>
        <p>In today’s competitive job market, sending out countless resumes often feels like shouting into the void. What if there was a platform that skipped the endless applications and put you directly in front of employers through <strong>AI-powered interviews</strong>? Enter <strong>RequireHire</strong> (<a href="https://www.requirehire.com/" target="_blank">requirehire.com</a>), India’s interview-first recruitment platform designed to connect talent with opportunities efficiently and fairly.</p>

        <p>RequireHire stands out by focusing on <strong>skills over paperwork</strong>. It’s not just another job board; it’s an interview-first ecosystem where candidates get verified, assessed, and matched with companies eager to hire. Whether you’re a fresh graduate in Jharkhand or an experienced professional in a metro city, this platform levels the playing field.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>What is RequireHire?</h2>
        <p>RequireHire is an AI-driven recruitment platform launched to address the frustrations of traditional job hunting in India. Unlike conventional portals that rely on resume databases or mass listings, RequireHire emphasizes <strong>direct interviews</strong>. Here’s what makes it unique:</p>

        <ul>
            <li><strong>AI-Powered Interviews</strong>: Candidates complete quick, skill-based AI interviews at their convenience, receiving instant scores and feedback.</li>
            <li><strong>Profile Verification</strong>: Only verified profiles are showcased, ensuring authenticity for both job seekers and employers.</li>
            <li><strong>Anonymized Matching</strong>: Your details stay private until you approve access, giving you control over who sees your full profile.</li>
            <li><strong>Pan-India Reach</strong>: With talent from over 50 cities, including emerging hubs like Jharkhand, it caters to diverse locations and roles in IT, data science, and more.</li>
            <li><strong>Free for Candidates</strong>: No hidden fees — it’s 100% free for job seekers, including premium tools like AI Resume Checker and Interview Prep.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Supported in <strong>English and Hindi</strong>, RequireHire is tailored for the Indian market, making it accessible for users across the country. Google recognizes it as a key player in “require hire” searches, directing users to this efficient hiring solution.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>How Does RequireHire Work?</h2>
        <p>Getting started on <a href="https://www.requirehire.com/" target="_blank">requirehire.com</a> is straightforward. Here’s a step-by-step guide to boost your engagement:</p>

        <ol>
            <li><strong>Sign Up and Build Your Profile</strong>: Create a free account and upload your details. Use the AI tools to optimize your resume and cover letter.</li>
            <li><strong>Search for Jobs</strong>: Browse thousands of verified openings by role, location (e.g., Jharkhand or pan-India), salary, and company. Filters make it easy to find the perfect fit.</li>
            <li><strong>Take the AI Interview</strong>: For roles that interest you, complete a short AI-powered interview. This assesses technical skills, communication, problem-solving, and cultural fit.</li>
            <li><strong>Get Scored and Feedback</strong>: Receive an instant AI-generated report with scores and personalized insights to improve.</li>
            <li><strong>Get Discovered</strong>: Top performers are ranked and visible to employers. When a company requests access, approve it to connect directly with HR for real interviews.</li>
        </ol>

        <p>For employers, it’s equally seamless: They browse ranked candidates, review structured summaries, and request connections — all while saving time on screening.</p>

        <p>This process ensures “proper engagement” by focusing on quality matches, reducing ghosting, and accelerating hires.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="benefits">
