            <li><strong>Skill-Based Feedback</strong>: Instant reports help you identify strengths and areas for improvement, making you more competitive.</li>
            <li><strong>Control and Privacy</strong>: Anonymized until you say yes, protecting your data.</li>
            <li><strong>Free Career Tools</strong>: AI Resume Checker, CV Pro, Cover Letter Generator, and Interview Prep are all complimentary.</li>
            <li><strong>Inclusive for All Levels</strong>: Perfect for freshers, students, and experienced pros, with special support for campus hiring.</li>
            <li><strong>Boosted Visibility</strong>: Verified profiles and AI scores make you stand out, increasing your chances of landing interviews.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Users report faster responses and higher success rates, turning “require hire” into a reality rather than a search term.</p>
